"{\"uid\": \"etonline.com-colin-jost-shares-hilarious-foot-update-after-exiting-as-olympics-correspondent-due-to-injury-and\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Colin Jostis sharing a \\\"foot update\\\" afterhaving to leave his post as NBC's Olympic swimming correspondentdue to an injury he sustained to his foot that led to a number of infections.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 70, \"end\": 73, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999926137662, \"rank\": 3.923369727956131e-09, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jost, 42, appeared in a video he posted to Instagram on Sunday, and delivered the update like a news anchor while standing on a\\u00a0Mediterranean beach.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.13779091552595e-19, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"'Dude, are you OK?'\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the no.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 text message I have received in the past 48 hours.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Usually followed by, 'Heard your foot fell off.'\\\"\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jost said in the video.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, I am actually fine!\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite what big media conspiracies would have you believe, I wasn't 'sent home' from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC simply looked at my food, declared me legally a leper, and exiled me here, to the island of Malta!\\\"\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999926137662, \"rank\": 3.923369727956131e-09, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.9999817964027673, \"rank\": 1.2512425486196421e-05, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now Malta does not have many Olympians competing this year, but it does have thousands of 15-year-old British kids competing to see who can black out the fastest, and somehow they are all winning,\\\" Jost continued.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.9999817964027673, \"rank\": 1.2512425486196421e-05, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}, {\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9781867761673768, \"rank\": 0.0221843380853232, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They also have this casino behind me, where I have blown the hundreds of dollars I have earned as a surfing correspondent.\\\"\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the real reason I am in Malta of course is because it was the site of 10 separate bubonic plague outbreaks,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.9999817964027673, \"rank\": 1.2512425486196421e-05, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So they thought I would fit right in.\\\"\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to thank the people of Tahiti for their warmth, their hospitality, their generosity and for only occasionally looking at my foot and\\u00a0and whispering 'Chupacabra!'\\\"\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999988349550187, \"rank\": 1.164824467641088e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 26, Jost shared aphotoof his bloodied foot on Instagramafter scraping it on a coral reef.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"score\": 0.9995924699143715, \"rank\": 0.00039135182839025213, \"text\": \"Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This might ruin my WikiFeet score but I just arrived in Tahiti for the surfing Olympics and the reef was excited to greet me,\\\" he joked in his caption.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999988349550187, \"rank\": 1.164824467641088e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Days later, he posted another pic of his foot -- this time covered in bandages -- after suffering a staph infection.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know it's going great when you have been to the Olympic medical tent more than any of the athletes,\\\" he cracked.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In his latest update, Jost shared a health update as well, joking, \\\"Rest assured, my foot is pretty much totally fine.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"score\": 0.9995924699143715, \"rank\": 0.00039135182839025213, \"text\": \"Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though I am not letting you look at it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After finishing up his sign-off from the beach in Malta, Jost awkwardly shuffled off, gingerly favoring his injured foot.\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2117, \"end\": 2122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.9999817964027673, \"rank\": 1.2512425486196421e-05, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last Tuesday, it wasannouncedthat Jost has taken on a headlining gig at the Fringe Festival in Rochester, New York, next month after palPete Davidsonbowed outto seek mental health treatment.\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2224, \"end\": 2228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"score\": 0.9995924699143715, \"rank\"